---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="partners — the keepers." description="Sponsorship options and the editorial firewall." current="partners">
  <div class="container container-narrow page">
    <p class="ui-label">sponsorship · capped, named, audited</p>
    <h1>reach a <em>saturday-morning</em> bay area readership.</h1>
    <p class="lead">Five thousand newsletter subscribers and growing. One issue every saturday. Caps on sponsor count per year so your placement matters.</p>

    <h2>the editorial firewall.</h2>
    <p>Sponsors do <em>not</em> pick stories. The editor who writes a best of list is named on the list. Promoted entries appear with a labeled badge and must still meet the editorial bar.</p>

    <h2>what we offer.</h2>
    <p>Four products. Specific pricing on request. We gate rates behind a conversation so we can match the placement to the partner.</p>
    <ul class="products">
      <li><strong>featured listing.</strong> Quarterly placement on a best of list. Foot-in-the-door tier.</li>
      <li><strong>sponsored profile.</strong> One saturday issue, your story told in the keeper voice. Cap two per quarter.</li>
      <li><strong>personal brand profile.</strong> Bespoke package: durable article, newsletter feature, social, listing inclusion. Cap one per quarter.</li>
      <li><strong>newsletter sponsorship.</strong> Sole sponsor of one saturday issue. Four-issue bundle minimum.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><a class="btn-primary" href="mailto:partners@sftimes.com">start a conversation →</a></p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page { padding-block: var(--s-9); }
  .page h1 {
    margin-block: var(--s-3) var(--s-5);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 30;
  }
  .page h1 :global(em) {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 80, 'WONK' 1;
  }
  .page h2 {
    margin-block: var(--s-7) var(--s-3);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 80, 'WONK' 1;
  }
  .page p em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 16, 'WONK' 1;
  }
  .page .lead { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: var(--s-6); max-width: 56ch; }
  .products { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .products li { padding: var(--s-4) 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block; background: var(--ink); color: var(--bg);
    padding: var(--s-3) var(--s-5); font-family: var(--font-ui); font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em; margin-top: var(--s-5);
    transition: background var(--t-fast) var(--ease-out);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--terracotta); }
</style>
